  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "To him they had regard,.... Which is repeated from the foregoing verse, for the sake of what follows: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "because that of a long time he had bewitched them with sorceries; or because he had, it may be for many years, astonished them with his magic arts, and the pranks he played in the use of them. ",
        "children": [
